#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calibrate Game Controller"
msgstr "Kalibrasikan Game Controller"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This module provides an interface to calibrate your game controller as well "
"as see which functions on your game controller are mapped to which logical "
"button or axis."
msgstr ""
"Modul ini menyediakan sebuah antarmuka untuk mengkalibrasi game controller-"
"mu sebagaimana yang tampak dengan fungsi-fungsinya pada game controller-mu "
"yang dipetakan di mana tombol logis dan poros."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of the game controller module"
msgstr "Ini adalah screenshot dari modul game controller"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "The game controller module"
msgstr "Modul game controller"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Device"
msgstr "Peranti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can see the logical location of the device. If you have more than "
"one game controller, you can also select which one to configure."
msgstr ""
"Di sini kamu bisa melihat lokasi logisnya peranti. Jika kamu mempunyai game "
"controller lebih dari satu, kamu juga bisa memilih salahsatu untuk "
"dikonfigurasikan."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If no game controller is automatically found on your computer and you know "
"that there is one attached, you can enter the correct device file here."
msgstr ""
"Jika tidak ada game controller yang secara otomatis ditemukan di komputermu "
"dan kamu tau ada satu yang tertancap, kamu bisa memasukkan file peranti yang "
"benar di sini."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Position"
msgstr "Posisi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The plotted location of the X and Y axes of the game controller's joystick. "
"Enable <guibutton>Show trace</guibutton> to plot the path of the joystick "
"from one point to another."
msgstr ""
"Lokasi yang diplot dari poros X dan Y si game controller. Fungsikan "
"<guibutton>Tampilkan jejak</guibutton> untuk memplot alur joystick dari satu "
"titik ke titik lainnya."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the joystick cannot reach every point on this graph, or if it does not "
"center correctly, you need to calibrate your device."
msgstr ""
"Jika joystick tidak dapat mencapai setiap titik pada grafik ini, atau jika "
"itu tidak terpusat dengan benar, kamu perlu mengkalibrasi perantimu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Buttons"
msgstr "Tombol"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A place to see the pressed state of buttons on your game controller and if "
"the buttons are mapped correctly. When a button is pressed, "
"<guilabel>PRESSED</guilabel> will appear next to the logical number (as the "
"computer sees it) of the button which was pressed."
msgstr ""
"Tempat untuk melihat status tombol yang ditekan pada game controller-mu dan "
"jika tombol dipetakan dengan benar. Saat tombol ditekan, teks "
"<guilabel>PRESSED</guilabel> akan muncul di sebelah angka logis (seperti "
"yang terlihat di komputer) dari tombol yang ditekan."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "Axes"
msgstr "Poros"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This displays the numerical values of the axis positions. 0 is centered and "
"the maximum and minimum values depend on the game controller and the "
"particular axis."
msgstr ""
"Ini mendisplaikan nilai numeriknya posisi poros. Nilai 0 adalah ditengah dan "
"nilai-nilai maksimum dan minimum tergantung pada game controller dan poros "
"tertentu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calibrate"
msgstr "Kalibrasikan"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on <guibutton>Calibrate</guibutton> will open a dialog to calibrate "
"every axis on your joysticks."
msgstr ""
"Mengeklik pada <guibutton>Kalibrasi</guibutton> akan membuka sebuah dialog "
"untuk mengkalibrasi setiap poros pada joystick-joystick-mu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Calibrating your game controller</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Mengkalibrasi game controller-mu</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Calibrating your game controller</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Mengkalibrasi game controller-mu</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each axis will have to be moved to the minimum position, then the center, "
"and finally the maximum position. A meter in the bottom left corner of the "
"dialog will help determine which way increases and which way decreases the "
"values."
msgstr ""
"Setiap poros akan dipindah ke posisi minimum, kemudian tengah, dan yang "
"terakhir posisi maksimum. Sebuah angka di pojok kiri bawah dari dialog akan "
"membantu menentukan cara mana menambah dan cara mana mengurangi nilai-"
"nilainya."

